Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:05.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}Broken and lost lies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:11.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}the last component somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:17.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}I look for it, and follow the distant stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:24.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}to the ends of a rainbow sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:39.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}Through the cracks faint light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:41.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}leaks into my vision to lure me onward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:46.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}and I walk my path as in a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:49.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}The growing strength of my bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}and my ability to redo it all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:59.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}will not let go of all my heart holds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}Help me retrieve it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:08.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}I will connect the bits and pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:12.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}and once I look at the ring they make,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}I will change it for my sake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:20.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}and spin it anew,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:24.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}so that I can be myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:31.77,Default,IKKIFAN,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.03,Default,IKKIFAN,0,0,0,,broke your promise, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.88,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.14,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:21.91,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.17,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.89,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,It's not cut, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.75,Default,ORION,0,0,5,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.91,Default,ORION,0,0,5,,It seemed like a fragment of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.13,Default,GIRL,0,0,5,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:42.31,Default,ORION,0,0,5,,Did those girls do that to you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:47.71,Default,ORION,0,0,5,,But cutting a girl's hair is criminal! Criminal, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.11,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.01,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Before I lost my memories, and even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.62,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.74,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,it seems inevitable that they'll cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:04.08,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,It's more than petty hatred. I feel like I'm despised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.96,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I could definitely feel their animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.25,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,They said "promise," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:12.91,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:17.36,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,It seems that before you lost your memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.88,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,you must've made a promise with those girls,{obviously}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:25.05,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,and since you lost your memories, you ended up breaking that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:30.02,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I doubt they'll tell us the whole story, even if we ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:35.31,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,They might even take advantage of your memory loss and lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:41.92,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,As such, I must still recommend that you keep your memory loss a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.87,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,The people you work with don't seem like bad people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:49.04,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,but we don't even know what your oldest friends, Toma and Shin, are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.09,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,And now that someone harbors animosity toward you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.67,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,there's no telling how information might leak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.60,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.88,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I don't know what promise I made to those girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.05,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,but I broke that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:11.68,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Because of that, I hurt someone or made them sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.88,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Are you all better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.62,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.74,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm not totally up to speed yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.09,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,It's okay. We'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.98,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,Sawa, you're so reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.93,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,No, Mine, you're helping out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.32,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I think we can trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.23,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.55,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,There's something different about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.93,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.52,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I thought everything was going well, but I spoke too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.97,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,If you asked me what it was, I couldn't tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.19,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,but something feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:59.43,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,She's been spacing out a lot lately, but then again, she's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.57,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Great cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.53,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.48,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,Today we're meeting about the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.05,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.99,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to go too, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.84,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Is everyone supposed to be at the meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.50,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.38,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,It's our orientation trip for part-timers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.36,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,so we talked about how we should all meet to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.98,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I meant, do you think everyone can come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.09,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:28.51,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,At first Shin said he couldn't make it because he was studying for exams, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:33.52,Default,SAKA,0,0,0,,Taking occasional breaks may improve the efficacy of your exam studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.39,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,So Shin said he'd come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.94,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,So in the end, we can all go. Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.08,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.28,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,{senpai}Hey, you don't look it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.21,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.51,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Three days and two nights on an island trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:58.26,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Is it all right for me to go in my current state?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.88,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,This first hurdle is set too high, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.48,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,It'll be challenging to not make any mistakes during the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.12,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,That said, it could also be a chance at getting your memories back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.58,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,so we should think optimistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.56,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.39,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.60,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.06,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,What have you been mumbling to yourself over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.56,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,Take this to table three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.44,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,A birthday cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.57,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,I haven't seen one of those in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:38.35,Default,SAWA/GIRL,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you. Happy birthday to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.18,Default,SAWA/GIRL,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:49.89,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.32,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,...killed a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.10,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,What was that? That was Shin, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.00,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Was that another memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.34,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}Killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.35,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.82,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.55,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.89,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,I hope it won't rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.52,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.01,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:25.02,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,There'd be no point, if it rained and you couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.92,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Couldn't see what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.96,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "see what?" It was {\i1}your{\i0} idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.82,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.93,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.78,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Shin's looking right at you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:42.40,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,It was you who said you wanted to see the Mnemid meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.40,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Just go along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.59,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.65,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.73,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.12,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,You're forgetting too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:59.70,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,According to the weekly weather report, it should be mostly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.19,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.77,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.20,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said I wanted to see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.34,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.49,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Are you all right with your studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm going because it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.00,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.59,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,By the way, Kento, you're a graduate student in math, right?{sup kyhz}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.35,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Why don't you have him teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.56,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but organize your questions beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.63,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,That way, I won't waste my time on meaningless problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.11,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:39.90,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like to begin our meeting concerning the island trip this weekend, August 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.23,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,To strengthen inter-staff relations at Meido no Hitsuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:47.49,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,I planned on bringing us together under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.84,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,But, well, let's leave out the serious talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.66,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,Everyone, please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.32,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Looks like we made it out okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.79,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,But there's so much I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:05.13,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,It might be inevitable that everyone thinks I'm acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.38,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,At the moment, Mine and Shin are particularly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.86,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,They look like they suspect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:18.32,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it might be a good idea to ask more questions that could give us hints about your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.40,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.89,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,It would be nice if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:29.29,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I said I'd do my best, but it's not enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.19,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:35.63,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,It's a huge help having you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.94,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I'm glad you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:42.39,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,But we can't seem to recover any helpful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.39,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.44,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.28,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,The light's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.28,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.79,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to space out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.91,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,This has happened before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.79,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,You don't remember me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.36,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.42,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.82,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Have you met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:25.04,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Just now, I felt something flutter in my chest.{GAAAAAAAY}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.19,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.59,Default,ORIN,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.20,Default,ORIN,0,0,0,,What a beautiful view!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:58.59,Default,ORIN,0,0,0,,Plus, this is my first time riding in one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.17,Default,PEOPLE,0,0,0,,Ah, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.36,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,What a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:25.97,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:34.39,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin's looking over at you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.01,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I wonder why. It looks like there's something he really wants to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.15,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Do you think he knows that you lost your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:59.32,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Wasn't it supposed to be clear this weekend with 0% chance of rain, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.91,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,That was the forecast during the week,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.74,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,but the weather changes rapidly.{as the writer demands}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.69,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:07.71,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,What a downpour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.72,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,Now, everyone. I think this rain will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.79,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,I don't see any sign of that. How do you figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.37,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,I can tell by the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.30,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.11,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Smell, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.01,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Can you really predict the weather by smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like it's going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:43.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You told me to promise you just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.71,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kento?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.16,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I wonder what the promise was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.90,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.13,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,It stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:59.39,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Wow, Waka was right! The rain really stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.72,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,It stopped just like he said it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.27,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,That's kind of amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.26,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.02,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,What kind of smell does rain have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.18,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:18.21,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,What is it? Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.15,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.19,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,You look like you've been daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.68,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can he tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:32.03,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Hey, let's ask him about the vision you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:39.93,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Um, as I was listening to the rain, I remembered the festival we went to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.05,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,There were lots of pretty wind chimes in the merchant stalls,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:49.27,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,and while it drizzled, you let me under your umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.06,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,He's so inexpressive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.96,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You remember, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.40,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,We were at a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.62,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.07,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,We're over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:07.16,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, Kento doesn't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:14.62,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,But all the visions you've seen up until now have been too disjointed, and there isn't anything connecting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.48,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,The people in them are always different, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.20,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.58,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.38,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if they're experiences I had before I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.22,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.55,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,While we wait for the meteor shower, let's play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.72,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Team air hockey, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.72,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,The first contenders are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.23,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Shin and Toma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.61,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,versus Kento and Ikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:47.35,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Shin, you're on offense, I'm on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.58,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Of course. There isn't any other formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.69,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:56.08,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Looks like {\i1}some{\i0} people are blurting out their strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.87,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're underestimating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:02.69,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Of course not. You're good at this kind of game, aren't you, Ikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.47,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,You're in the table tennis club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.74,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Wrong. I'm in the darts circle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.79,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,I'm good at almost any game that uses my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.73,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's pretty much all games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.39,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,You don't need a strategy meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.41,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,It's already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.69,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,I'll come up with the plan, and Ikkyu will do the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:22.78,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Hey, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.35,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Ikkyu? He means Ikki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.35,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't have to be polite and reveal our strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.30,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Is that a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:31.20,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now it's fair. We'll just show them that they'll still lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.34,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,His real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:30.65,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Either way, it doesn't suit him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.35,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,I'm the one who has to do the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.20,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Not that I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.66,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,They sure talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.41,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,Well, we don't plan on losing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:45.42,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Okay, it looks like both teams are ready, so let the game begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.76,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.64,Default,KENTO,0,0,0,,Show them a false opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.69,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Kento and Ikki win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ikki is seriously just too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:13.62,Default,TOMA,0,0,0,,No, Kento's flawless strategies are really something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:16.24,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Damn... I don't think I can win in a game that uses hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.38,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I know, cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.79,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's play poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.96,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:26.22,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,But like I said before, I'm good at any game that uses my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:31.09,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Well, poker uses hands in a different sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:35.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm seriously starting to think there's no winning against Ikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.47,Default,IKKI,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.35,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I'm glad we came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.83,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,That's true. Thank you, Orion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.22,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,But I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.60,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm sure I couldn't've done this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.38,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Just having you here is a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.18,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.24,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You know, I'm happy that I'm with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:02.25,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I know getting your memories back is the top priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:07.12,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,but I'm happy I get to experience all these new things with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:08.77,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\i1}Orion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.50,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.06,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,It's our turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.38,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:19.19,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Let's beat the crap out of Waka and Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.14,Default,SAWA,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.52,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.52,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,The Mnemid meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:41.62,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,It is said that those who see it will etch wonderful memories into their hearts.{DEEP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.02,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,I hope that tonight will be a wonderful memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.49,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,Mr. Manager, how much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.61,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,Just a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.30,Default,MINE,0,0,0,,You said that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.80,Default,WAKA,0,0,0,,This time I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.30,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,This is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.86,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.97,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.99,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You tried hard at air hockey, so maybe you've used up all your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.62,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,But good job beating the manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.68,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Yeah. I surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:10.44,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,The manager's puck disappeared for a second, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.44,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You did well to hit it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.19,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I had my eyes closed the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.25,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,What? So you hit that by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.07,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Well, it was fun either wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.70,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're exhausted, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.73,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Not... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.28,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Come on, just give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.68,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:43.35,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.35,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.68,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,I think being alone with him is a bad idea right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:52.32,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,We don't know what he's going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.62,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You have to make up an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:58.31,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Um... We should catch up to the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:01.28,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,or they'll worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.38,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.54,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.38,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,I'm fine. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,{\i1}I killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.67,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,{\i1}...killed a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.37,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,Now I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.31,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,I guess I should take this to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.40,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.47,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:44.53,Default,HYOU,0,0,0,,Because this is where he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:36.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,How long are you going to sleep for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.27,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.04,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's already ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.26,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.65,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,August 1st?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.27,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're half asleep, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.15,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What are you spacing out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.23,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let me snap you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:12.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}My vision wavers like a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}The ones I see daily
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}have no true color or light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}Hear the distant roll of thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}That's my love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}This world is made of melted snow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:55.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}I held out my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:22:00.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}Where are we in this darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:06.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}I've woken up, and nothing happens
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}Wake me up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:14.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}Warm rays of light strike my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}The wind bids to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}outside the window
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:21.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:25.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}I force open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:30.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}and a little voice crosses my consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:34.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)\blur5}The girl in me sings to my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{part c}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:45.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to freak out in embarrassment today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:53.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You are {\i1}really{\i0} out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:58.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll sign the forms to get you discharged, so get dressed by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.63,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,When I get back, I'll come in without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:02.49,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:06.71,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Discharge? What is he talking about?{the vaginal kind}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:10.03,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Orion, I think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:14.70,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:20.56,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:22.83,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:24.88,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:27.86,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Do you know the trick to winning in air hockey?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:29.90,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,To maintain a strong defense, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.03,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,You can't let your opponent score a single point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.82,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,The best offense is a strong defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.66,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Or is it the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:39.31,Default,ORION,0,0,0,,Also, boys shouldn't ride in swan boats together.
